#40000
The Greed Island Starting Point~
   You are near a tall stilt hut where new players arrive from.  A spiral
staircase under the hut is how people come down to Greed Island, but it
is impossible to go back up while Eeta carefully keeps it locked.  In every
direction you can see a vast green plain with mountains in the background.
