#40010
A Road Through The Plains~
You are on a dust-covered southwest-to-northwest road through the eastern plains.
An occasional hunter or adventurer can be seen, heading to or from the forest.
To the northeast you see a walled city atop the hills, and to the southwest the
road heads back to the plains of the starting point.
To the east stands a giant tree with so many branches along its trunk that it is
easy to climb.
~
